name: Colossus Wanders Paradise
description: When Colossus journeyed into Elysium he met with a cascading landscape before him ~ Animated from paintings by Jean-Léon Gérôme, William Turner (Valley Of Aosta) and Gustav Dore - Poetry by William Blake “Jerusalem” and Johann Christoph Friedrich Schiller “The Greatness Of The World” ~ Produced and performed by Laurence Fuller ~ This reading was recorded live during the Here And Now live HEN event by Wide Awake Beets @LaurenceFuller
